.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人係藍貓rc相認先 我係隊伍語音頻2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bef4e14b1c4fff00c2787c15f385798b1c4a0fc","tid":194711,"uid":4929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:25:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>星夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個斷斷續續玩左幾年<br />\n引怪爆怪依個設計師真係好爽</blockquote><br />\n不過依家睇返其實幾悶,D職唔平衡搞到開組離離去去都係要嗰幾個職,其他就食晒屎除非你FD組,真係好佩服當年可以由朝爆到晚</blockquote><br />\n以前玩唔厭 每日綠頻組隊<br />\n見到有人招人升都仲要鬥快跑去<br />\n又要搶地盤唔好爆親人啲怪<br />\n<br />\n星眼果啲細地圖又勁多人一齊升真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗返以前玩引真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n逐隻逐隻拉,又唔可以跑太遠,否則就跑散晒D怪要重頭拉返,真係血都嘔埋出黎<br />\n自己嗰個職又唔係話太引得(聖劍士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ),一引太多就有去冇回都似<br />\n不過overall嗰種感覺係近年D網遊搵唔返嘅"},{"pid":"54d8fab6e6b214ece89f52333edc8154f197f2a6","tid":194711,"uid":104499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:47:12.000Z","msg":"真係有心想玩藍貓SER既 RC PM巴神,話唔定有裝送<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f86cbff2c00386c79f06d6a020585a271af873","tid":194711,"uid":82792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係有心想玩藍貓SER既 RC PM巴神,話唔定有裝送<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n玩反幾日 但妹難升lv"},{"pid":"27b5ffd3f810f8a89919e048d33905c48ca0b36c","tid":194711,"uid":82792,"like":0,"di